&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Displacement&lt;/strong&gt;: Automation may lead to job losses in certain sectors, creating a need for workforce reskilling and transition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complexity of Integration&lt;/strong&gt;: Integrating AI systems with existing processes may be complex and time-consuming.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="practical-use-cases-of-ai-automation-in-2026"&gt;Practical Use Cases of AI Automation in 2026&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id="case-study-1-ai-in-retail"&gt;Case Study 1: AI in Retail&lt;/h4&gt;
